1:22.000Z","msg":"軒仔屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9474a3aadf2f8dea68cb8d599c4c4474a09ae5a5","tid":297860,"uid":91482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T21:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳柏宇係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但同張敬軒仲有一段距離喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都岩既 蠢左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順手搭下第二條線<br />\n定用全盛時期既側田同勁軒比會好啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4093e844acd92e2892f1dbc1322cb88653fe839","tid":297860,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T21:53:41.000Z","msg":"柏宇唱下口水歌就好聽既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da43fe343bfee4c40acf0a10fb63897d333ef13","tid":297860,"uid":91482,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T22:21:53.000Z","msg":"雖則Level有差別 <br />\n但問心兩個啲Live都好正<br />\n以依加啲歌手黎講 <br />\n佢地靠現場都已經好穩好有水準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係勁軒可以用 '高質無敵' 黎形容多層姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42b592e658748b02aa995b651775a231f23b418","tid":297860,"uid":26977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:37:48.000Z","msg":"兩個都好正<br />\n但我正皮咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcb62883ec3f8688b147ffb75bdbc93bab8a095","tid":297860,"uid":10859,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"真係要出廁田先比到"},{"pid":"3f796c15b07f1489199e68f06b8d592c600fbb06","tid":297860,"uid":31215,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"側田都比唔到張敬軒<br />\n側田成日會好唔啱mood咁演繹一隻